claim.claim-text:
17. A user equipment device comprising:
a channel feedback report generator operable to generate a first set of measured channel feedback information (CFI), including a first measured rank, and a second set of measured CFI, including a second measured rank;
processing logic operable to use the first measured rank process a first CFI report and the second measured rank to process a second CFI report; and
transmission circuitry operable to transmit the first CFI report on a first communication channel, and to transmit the second CFI report on a second communication channel;
wherein the first and second measured rank are independent of each other.
